未必舉行的盛事宣傳上，是否錯配。程鼎一指，旅發局的確計劃贊助部分大型盛事項目以作宣傳，但會詳細審視情況，小心運用預算。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528193-20200525.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528193-20200525.htm&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3i9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=971d589d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528193-20200525.htm&h=99965fe9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528193-20200525.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">疫情不是已經完結了嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:49:58.000Z","msg":"免費週會唔會更吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家話葉劉叻啲定係我？"},{"pid":"a3bff65f6d1a99027a1142af6e903a8576d91e9d","tid":2034244,"uid":332752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:50:07.000Z","msg":"成日都搞減價吸引人去商場<br />\n然後又派黑警黎掃場罰$2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係減價係假 罰$2000幫補正苦係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔識分啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3401da4cfed50290d541e6c8e5bf7ccd6030f8cf","tid":2034244,"uid":6213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:51:41.000Z","msg":"同意呀 減啦<br />\n好想同班狗shopping"},{"pid":"0ad008fd190aa5a5a6a743632065a31c4ab38b7f","tid":2034244,"uid":48492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"姐姐想買新皮草先咁講咋"},{"pid":"7f8b301c5e38f89ccfd4e45477cbf6fd65bf00a1","tid":2034244,"uid":233332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"點解硬係要吸引旅客? <br />\n而唔係藉住呢波推動返本土嘅經濟圈同店家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\